.DT
debug_printf
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
debug_printf

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
debug_printf -  This method will generate a debug inform for any creators in the room where it is generated.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void debug_printf(string fmt,
mixed args ...)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^all%^RESET%^ - printf style parameters
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun/debug.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will generate a debug inform for any creators in the room
where it is generated.  It will always attempt to identify the room
that the event should be sent to.

.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
#ifdef DEBUG
  debug_printf("Error, player is: %O\n", player);
#endif

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
printf

.EP

